window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>At this magic academy, corpses roam campus and spirits haunt the halls. </b><br> <br> College student Nadine is done with other students tormenting her about her powers. To show her classmates what she's capable of, Nadine teams up with her two best friends and her boyfriend, Lucas, to compete in the school's annual magical sporting event. Join the team as they fight zombies, face ghosts, and brew potions on their quest to win the spooky Haunted Tournament. </p> <p><i>This short story follows characters from the Hidden Legends: College of Witchcraft series and may contain spoilers. This series is part of the Hidden Legends Universe, which features college-aged protagonists attending magical academies, dual points-of-view, disabled and diverse main characters, and steamy, empowering romances.</i></p>"; 
